    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Burnout 🔥 has never been so much fun!</strong>   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >IT Startup: Tech Fodder is a dev themed Roguelike Deckbuilder. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play Developer Cards, upgrade them and watch out for burnout! Sabotage your opponents or steal their Developers. Craft a unique deck and <strong>squeeze out your employees to win the next Project Battle!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704120/extras/4bff8557d110bd0cbf12124c8aa02a14.avif?t=1741772393\" width=535 height=340 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704120/extras/cbec2eec3c5451b07a2f305f02b9a9e8.avif?t=1741772393\" width=525 height=88 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704120/extras/bc43a24e6794374cedf78a41389c7d9e.poster.avif?t=1741772393\" width=540 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704120/extras/bc43a24e6794374cedf78a41389c7d9e.webm?t=1741772393\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704120/extras/bc43a24e6794374cedf78a41389c7d9e.mp4?t=1741772393\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704120/extras/2efa0cf230fcd12ff3b6c3eac4dea94f.avif?t=1741772393\" width=539 height=402 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704120/extras/bae2b780f87355b701e6582c7a99acf0.avif?t=1741772393\" width=432 height=143 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Master card synergies</strong>, to win all the Project Battles during your run. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Unlock </strong> new starter decks and modules, to get a fresh run experience. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Build</strong> your perfect deck, to defeat the final boss. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Pick</strong> the right modificator modules that go well with your deck.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become a <strong>good company</strong>, or a <strong>well oiled employee meat grinder</strong> with unpaid interns<strong>.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Strategically ban a boss option</strong>, to gain a tactical advantage in the final <strong>Boss Project Battle</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collect</strong> cards from boosters, to play a run with your custom constructed deck (the constructed deck option is there for you to experiment with fringe builds, craft a custom challenge, or just have fun with the most OP one turn win combos).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Engage</strong> in ridiculous meetings.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Replay your past boss encounters</strong>, to reminisce the builds you once managed to assemble.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Adjust</strong> difficulty settings for your preferred gaming experience (from &quot;Relaxed&quot; for a casual experience, to &quot;Unfair&quot; for the ultimate challenge).  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704120/extras/bfb20786106e5db332ff387ab592bbee.avif?t=1741772393\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704120/extras/210f74c5914f78d7ec3616137de378f8.poster.avif?t=1741772393\" width=540 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704120/extras/210f74c5914f78d7ec3616137de378f8.webm?t=1741772393\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704120/extras/210f74c5914f78d7ec3616137de378f8.mp4?t=1741772393\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
